FUNCTION 
display emoji
activate lights

INPUT
wear mask
wear bracelet / band
display emoji
turn on lights

IF happy emoji is selected,
display smiley face & turn on green light

IF sad emoji is selected,
display sad face & turn on yellow light

IF neutral emoji is selected,
display straight face & turn on blue light

IF heart emoji is selected,
display beating hearts & turn on red light

IF rainbow is selected,
turn on rainbow lights 

END IF
RETURN
